      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. every single day it’s just more destruction and more heatwaves and more extinctions. it feels like we’re just watching a slow motion train wreck and there’s nothing anyone can actually do to stop it. it feels so pointless to even try to plan a future or care about anything when the world is basically already dead.",
